Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.50,Italics,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,She should be at the temple at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.87,Main,Monk,0000,0000,0000,,The line to see the Lady Cleric is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.01,Main,Monk,0000,0000,0000,,Please have your ticket in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.51,Main,People walla,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I feel alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.76,Main,People walla,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels so much lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:39.79,Italics,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's working hard again \Ntoday. Hopefully not too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.92,Flashback,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,I believe there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.35,Flashback,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,If we find a cleric who can exorcise evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:52.11,Flashback,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,But she rarely takes on jobs \Nto remove curse-based skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.70,Flashback,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,There may be some reason behind it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.88,Flashback,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm her best friend, \Nand she won't even tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.27,Main,Monk 2,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Cleric...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:09.88,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.55,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, but please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:13.71,Main,Monk 2,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.02,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.80,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:33.40,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,It appears as though you're \Nworking too hard, Lady Cleric.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:35.47,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:38.86,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the greeting for someone \Nwho's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:42.30,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:50.02,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the very capable receptionist \Nfrom the guild doing here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:53.09,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask this when I know you're tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.99,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,but I needed to discuss \Nsomething important with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:33.67,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day that Lola is going \Nto introduce us to this cleric.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.95,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I had some time before we \Nwere supposed to meet up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.51,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to get some \Nadvice from my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.91,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,"Hidden dungeon only I can enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.31,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Let me train in secret to become \Nthe strongest in the world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.70,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:01.72,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,563)\an1\bord1.25\blur1\pos(38,310)}#04 {\fscx90}"The Untainted Cleric"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.05,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hmphity hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.75,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}M-Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.51,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.99,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you haven't come see me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:10.14,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it's been about two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.11,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.73,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to come sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.44,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,but I ran into a little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.55,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A duke's daughter with a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.63,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:29.67,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a curse-based skill, \Nit might have to do with her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:33.21,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Her family? You mean something \Nto do with her ancestors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.46,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it happens all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.36,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,There's a skill to curse one's descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.09,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:46.29,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need over 10,000 LP to Get Creative \Nenough to create the skill to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:50.69,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably best if you let \Nthat cleric girl handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.23,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Right. That's what I plan on doing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.07,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the Lady Cleric is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:05:00.50,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,If she has the skill to exorcise things, \Nshe's probably at least part elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.18,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,An elf, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.86,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see them very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.69,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,It's great to fulfill some of \Nyour desires with other species.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:10.03,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get lots of extra LP with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.24,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.49,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta go for the glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.00,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:23.26,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, Master, what would you \Ndo to earn about 10,000 LP?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.04,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in my case... Here. \NI'll whisper it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.22,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:37.10,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,...to get their body extra sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.71,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,...tie down their...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.86,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,...and while they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.95,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll have 10,000 LP in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.88,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I'm kidding. You're so cute, Noir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.25,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's totally messing with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.25,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't be able to \Nget 10,000 that quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:03.07,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,but I can teach you a skill \Nthat'll be super useful in gaining LP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.96,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:11.48,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let your awesome master \NOlivia fill you in on the deets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.61,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.73,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,And now, for those deets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.48,Main,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get the best bang for your buck! \NThis forbidden skill is...
