Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.16,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:47.87,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about that is terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.57,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure as a cleric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.69,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you lift a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.83,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,You never told me that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.48,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't tell you. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.61,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:09.49,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been hanging out \Nwith you this whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:12.21,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,without realizing something that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.88,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.90,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Some best friend! It pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.58,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad that I was so clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.60,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:28.00,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't realize how \Nmuch you were suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.91,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this, Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:35.81,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,You always put others before yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.36,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Lola...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.88,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Rely on me... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.32,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Luna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:44.87,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.00,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Lola... Luna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.94,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,There's something great about these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.46,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.90,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,You ended up witnessing \Nsuch an embarrassing scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.52,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. It was a feast for my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.78,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Er, I was very moved by you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.69,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:21.09,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,If we try to save Miss Maria, \Nthen Luna will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.12,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.38,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't completely hopeless yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:35.13,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to make this work \Nwithout any casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:43.13,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I just gave it a shot, \Nand took a look at Luna's Lift Curse skill.
