Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:10.41,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way to save Miss Maria \Nwithout having to sacrifice Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.75,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Noir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.62,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:19.75,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have quite \Nenough LP to use this skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.80,Main,Three,0000,0000,0000,,LP?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.81,Text_Box_Text,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(314,1)\pos(416,302)\shad2}Lacking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.06,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious foods...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.81,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Making money and satisfying \Nworldly desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:36.07,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,And doing exciting things with \Nattractive members of the opposite sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.71,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:42.83,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my Get Creative \Nor Editor skills without LP.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.58,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you can't make an omelet \Nwithout breaking a few eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:54.21,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway! Can you think of a way \Nfor me to get 2,000 more LP?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.53,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe something \Nthat'll increase Luna's finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.48,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.80,Main,Luna,0000,0000,0000,,I highly doubt there's \Nanything that convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.86,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,But there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.74,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:10.72,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,A certain noble holds the perfect event \Nfor this occasion every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.44,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,The next time it will be held is this weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.40,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll make it just in time to lift the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.10,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of event is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.06,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.11,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,It's called...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.46,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,The Harem Pride Event!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:30.14,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, my dudes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:35.84,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, another ten that \NI'm jealous of... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:42.62,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be meeting some reckless scoundrels \Nwho'll be showing off their hot girlfriends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.72,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,for a chance at one million rels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.24,Main,Crowd walla,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.39,Main,Crowd walla,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.47,Main,Crowd walla,0000,0000,0000,,Those lucky bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.72,Main,Crowd walla,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:58.25,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,So vent all the stress you can at \Nthe sight of these shitty normies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:05.15,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the host of this event has been \Nbetrayed by women countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:10.77,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,And the gentlemen who have gathered \Nhere have experienced something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:13.90,Main,Lola,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them, apparently, \Ndon't have any lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.72,Main,Crowd A,0000,0000,0000,,Death to hot guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.77,Main,Crowd B,0000,0000,0000,,Screw harems!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.63,Main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Harems are unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:26.63,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't a pride event... \NThis is slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.47,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, my dudes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:34.31,Main,Peppero,0000,0000,0000,,Let the Harem Pride Event commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:47.36,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I want to go home now...
