Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:30.16,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:34.10,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.10,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing, Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.64,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is just... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.39,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I was just fixing your sheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.98,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,They seem messier than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.55,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm just going \Nto sleep in them as-is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.35,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:53.52,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... we're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:56.78,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,We used to sleep together \Nlike this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.50,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:06.97,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, hello? Alice is your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:10.42,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... my LP would go up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:13.92,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
